<header>
<h1><a href="/presentations">Presentations</a> → TEDxNUS - 9 stories in 18 minutes</h1>
<p class="postdate">Length: <strong>22 minutes.</strong> Date recorded: 2010-10</p>
</header>
<p><strong>9 short stories to a TEDx crowd at the National University of Singapore.</strong></p>

<p>
I was asked at the last minute to speak at a TEDx conference the National University of Singapore.
I didn't have time to prepare a big 20-minute talk, so I shared nine of my best little 2-minute stories.
</p><p>
Explanation of the opening minute:
The two talks right before me were about evolution and insect penises.
I couldn't resist a punchline. ☺
</p>
